metadata.name: Deer Club Exclusive Pass #270
metadata.description: Deer Club Exclusive PASS is a unique PASS collection consisting of a very special series of only 700 pieces by LasMeta VR Poker Gaming Platform to provide its holders many benefits, primarily passive income, and VIP access to gaming platform. Also DCE PASS holders have the right to 1 free mint slot for the Mystery Box NFT collection, which includes game costumes and items of the LasMeta VR Gaming Platform
